 Adding '90s Hit 'Bitch' Songwriters to Credits|last=Stutz|first=Colin|date=June 15, 2018|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=June 24, 2018}}</ref>\n\n'''Notes'''\n* {{sup|{{note|a|[a]}}}} signifies an additional vocal producer.\n* {{sup|{{note|b|[b]}}}} signifies an additional producer.\n\n==Personnel==\n'''Production'''\n* [[Management]]&nbsp;\u2013 Adam Mersel\n* [[Artists and repertoire|A&R]]&nbsp;\u2013 Jeff Levin\n* Mitch McCarthy &nbsp;\u2013 [[Audio mixing (recorded music)|mixing]] (tracks 1\u20135, and 7\u201313)\n* [[Manny Marroquin]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Audio mixing (recorded music)|mixing]] (track 6)\n* Michelle Mancini&nbsp;\u2013 [[Audio mastering|mastering]]\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-2}}\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2018)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br /> position\n|-\n{{album chart|Australia|19|artist=Bebe Rexha|album=Expectations|rowheader=true|accessdate=June 30, 2018}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Austria|71|artist=Bebe Rexha|album=Expectations|rowheader=true|accessdate=July 5, 2018}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Flanders|53|artist=Bebe Rexha|album=Expectations|rowheader=true|accessdate=June 29, 2018}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Wallonia|73|artist=Bebe Rexha|album=Expectations|rowheader=true|accessdate=June 29, 2018}}\n|-\n{{album chart|BillboardCanada|14|artist=Bebe Rexha|rowheader=true|accessdate=July 3, 2018}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Czech|60|date=201826|rowheader=true|accessdate=July 6, 2018}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Netherlands|58|artist=Bebe Rexha|album=Expectations|rowheader=true|accessdate=June 29, 2018}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Germany4|55|id=357087|artist=Bebe Rexha|album=Expectations|rowheader=true|accessdate=June 29, 2018}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Ireland2|40|artist=Bebe Rexha|rowheader=true|accessdate=June 30, 2018}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand Heatseeker Albums ([[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=4494|title=NZ He